Form Attributes Explained

-------------Required Attributes

required - Makes field mandatory

pattern - Validates input format (regex)

min/max - Sets number/date range limits

accept - Specifies allowed file types



-------------Input Types for Validation
type="email" - Validates email format

type="url" - Validates URL format

type="number" - Only allows numbers

type="date" - Provides date picker

---------------Real-time Features (Browser Built-in)
Instant validation on input

Error messages for invalid data

Date picker interface

File type filtering

Required field highlighting














